==========
 BIRTHDAY 
==========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

manage birthday data

| 

  manage birthdays 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *age (oud)*

    :description: age <nick> .. show how old <nick> is

    :permissions: USER .. WEB

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !age dunker
        <output> can't find user for bart@gozerbot.org


2) *bd (jarig)*

    :description: bd [<nr|user>] .. show birthdays for this month or show birthday of <nick>

    :permissions: USER .. WEB

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bd
        <output> no birthdays this month



    ::

        <user> !bd dunker
        <output> can't find user for bart@gozerbot.org


3) *bd-del (deljarig)*

    :description: delete birthday data

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bd-del
        <output> no birthday known for test


4) *bd-set (setbd)*

    :description: bd-set <date> .. set birthday

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !bd-set 3-11-1967
        <output> birthday set


